{"tid":2378349,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大指控學生會「不當」辦周梓樂悼念會 懲罰會長及內務副會長休學1學期","createTime":"2021-01-24T11:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T13:59:56.000Z","uid":29836,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48725ce90743ff514c7f439c75348831e9153275","tid":2378349,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"科大男生周梓樂2019年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突期間，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲。科大學生會早前為周同學逝世舉行半年悼念會，豈料遭校方秋後算賬，有學生會幹事被科大學生紀律委員會褫奪使用校園設施的權利半年、強制執行75小時校園服務令，以及留下紀律處分紀錄；學生會會長及內務副會長更被勒令休學一個學期。學生會對裁決表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n校方教務處去年8月曾以電郵，指控學生會數宗不當行為，包括舉辦周同學逝世半年悼念會、青蛙路補油及於學生會告示板張貼文宣。委員會曾要求學生會幹事作出書面解釋，並傳召幹事會成員到會上答辯。<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/HTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FHTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCLVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=120667b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FHTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI&h=d9b7ad90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/HTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蝌大又贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406a625754b4d0d0ff08906dc12b44ac2a20d8db","tid":2378349,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"屎遺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d9a16b05149a7875f858c06c5b9289a54d22a0","tid":2378349,"uid":29836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c